ShutdownManager<T extends Comparable> - Interface in com.facebook.lifecycle
allows for objects to register shutdown hooks used instead of direct shutdown hooks in order to manage the order they are called The idea here is that on startup, we register the Thread this provides as a hook in case the JVM is killed.
ShutdownManagerImpl<T extends Enum> - Class in com.facebook.lifecycle
